  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.thoughtbot.expandablerecyclerview.listeners.ExpandCollapseListener, com.thoughtbot.expandablerecyclerview.listeners.OnGroupClickListener

    public class RequestsTabAdapter
extends com.thoughtbot.expandablerecyclerview.ExpandableRecyclerViewAdapter<RequestsTabAdapter.RequestGroupViewHolder,RequestsTabAdapter.RequestsViewHolder>
    This is an Expandable Recycler Adapter The RequestGroupViewHolder determines the view of the Groups. i.e. "Accepted" and "Pending" The RequestsViewHolder determines the view of the Requests in each of these groups
